flex means set element flexiblly in a row.

=> display flex always applying in parent element.

which is only effected while applying flex 
property list => 

1. flex-grow (child)
2. flex-shrink (child)
3. flex-basis (child)
4. flex (child)

5. flex-direction (parent)
6. flex-wrap (parent)
7. flex-flow (parent)

8. row-gap (parent)
9. column-gap (parent)
10. gap (parent)

11. justify-content (parent) horizontal effect 

12. align-items (parent) vertical effect
13. align-self (child) vertical effect 
14. align-content (parent) vertical effect